  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/30ad5ac5957251d0ed86be657fa1287a.avif?t=1730198873\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Twisted Logic: Abbotsfield </strong>is a first-person psychological horror puzzle game where logic puzzles meet atmospheric exploration. You're an Exorcist from the Office of Unexplained Phenomena who must use case files handed over to you (accessed via an in-game link) in order to identify specific items in a derelict house and exorcise the demonic force haunting you. You have one hou<strong>r.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't get it twisted: </strong>Solve complex document-based logic puzzles by downloading case files and reports left by your colleagues. These files are accessed through an in-game link, and contain the details needed to obtain the correct objects from the house needed to perform the exorcism. You can also take hints by consulting an in-game Ouija board.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Home sweet home: </strong>Unravel the story of the Abbotsfield family through environmental exploration, revealing reports, and cryptic messages. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bring a friend: </strong>Play solo for an immersive and intense experience, or gather a group of friends and work together on the puzzles.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>Can you solve the logic puzzles, obtain the correct items, and exorcise the demon before time runs out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/4628b3703a5fe85a4efce3d6f64b206c.poster.avif?t=1730198873\" width=752 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/4628b3703a5fe85a4efce3d6f64b206c.webm?t=1730198873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/4628b3703a5fe85a4efce3d6f64b206c.mp4?t=1730198873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/21622277b72330d1fd7721cdc77c631c.poster.avif?t=1730198873\" width=658 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/21622277b72330d1fd7721cdc77c631c.webm?t=1730198873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/21622277b72330d1fd7721cdc77c631c.mp4?t=1730198873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong> </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/30ad5ac5957251d0ed86be657fa1287a.avif?t=1730198873\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Twisted Logic: Abbotsfield </strong>is a first-person psychological horror puzzle game where logic puzzles meet atmospheric exploration. You're an Exorcist from the Office of Unexplained Phenomena who must use case files handed over to you (accessed via an in-game link) in order to identify specific items in a derelict house and exorcise the demonic force haunting you. You have one hou<strong>r.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't get it twisted: </strong>Solve complex document-based logic puzzles by downloading case files and reports left by your colleagues. These files are accessed through an in-game link, and contain the details needed to obtain the correct objects from the house needed to perform the exorcism. You can also take hints by consulting an in-game Ouija board.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Home sweet home: </strong>Unravel the story of the Abbotsfield family through environmental exploration, revealing reports, and cryptic messages. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bring a friend: </strong>Play solo for an immersive and intense experience, or gather a group of friends and work together on the puzzles.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>Can you solve the logic puzzles, obtain the correct items, and exorcise the demon before time runs out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/4628b3703a5fe85a4efce3d6f64b206c.poster.avif?t=1730198873\" width=752 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/4628b3703a5fe85a4efce3d6f64b206c.webm?t=1730198873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/4628b3703a5fe85a4efce3d6f64b206c.mp4?t=1730198873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/21622277b72330d1fd7721cdc77c631c.poster.avif?t=1730198873\" width=658 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/21622277b72330d1fd7721cdc77c631c.webm?t=1730198873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261060/extras/21622277b72330d1fd7721cdc77c631c.mp4?t=1730198873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong> </p>",
